JSONDecoder - Class in utils.json
This class is responsible for the deserialization (JSON -> Java) of JSON Messages being in their String representation.
It makes use of the Gson library.
JSONDecoder() - Constructor for class utils.json.JSONDecoder
 
JSONEncoder - Class in utils.json
This class is responsible for the serialization (Java -> JSON) of JSONMessage Objects.
It makes use of the Gson library.
JSONEncoder() - Constructor for class utils.json.JSONEncoder
 
JSONMessage - Class in utils.json.protocol
This class is the wrapper class for all JSON messages of the protocol.
